  <summary date="2019-08-22T20:24:48Z" status="Introduced in House">Hear Our Heroes Act of 2017

This bill establishes a presumption of service-connection for veterans with permanent hearing loss, tinnitus, or both, who served on active duty in combat or in a military occupational specialty in which they were exposed to a high level of acoustic trauma.</summary>
